NAME
    B::Hooks::AtRuntime::OnlyCoreDependencies - it is just B::Hooks::AtRuntime
    but with only core dependencies

DESCRIPTION
    You probably want B::Hooks::AtRuntime.

    I just created this version because I didn't want dependencies on
    Sub::Name, Module::Build, and Test::Exports.

SEE ALSO
    B::Hooks::AtRuntime

AUTHOR
    Toby Inkster <tobyink@cpan.org>, though almost all the code is directly
    taken from B::Hooks::AtRuntime by Ben Morrow <ben@morrow.me.uk>.

